xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Consider the case where a Pedestrian or Cyclist is obeying the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">law</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> and is injured or killed by a motorist.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">As a starting point, that motorist </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">shall</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> automatically lose their</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> driving licence for the period that the victim is disabled.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">So</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> if the pedestrian or cyclist is disabled for a year the motorist will lose their licence for a year.</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">If the victim is killed the driver will never drive again.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">This is a starting penalty; the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">re may need to be bigger penalties.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">And remember, I AM A MOTORIST</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> but</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt"> it is the motorist who has the lethal machine.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">Also if a pedestrian is killed or injured by a cyclist, the cyclist will be banned from cycling for the period.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:12pt; font-style:italic">November 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p></div></body></html>